show.description: A struggling young man unlocks mysterious powers that plunge him into a ruthless world of corporate betrayal and deadly foes. With unexpected allies by his side, he must master his abilities before they consume him. A high-stakes saga of power, survival, and uncovering the truth behind the gift that could change everything. Watch now!
